3334037316.resolved_title: The Ultimate Guide for Flyer Size and Design
3334037316.excerpt: Although it may sound obsolete, a flyer is still one of the most effective and inexpensive ways to promote a business. They are also very easy to distribute. So, if you want your flyers to be impactful, you have to make sure you choose the right size, the right font, colors, and message.
